I see cool data and algorithm visualizations all the time,[^cool-vis-creators] but I've never really tried making any of my own.
Today's [Advent of Code](https://adventofcode.com/2025/day/4) problem seemed to lend itself to visualization fairly well, so I decided to give it a shot!

